<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_114" id="56v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_114_r2l16">Hercʒog Ernſten von Öſterreich </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_114_r2l17">Gnedıger <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> / Als vvir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>durchleuhtik<ex>eit</ex></expan> voꝛmals <expan>verſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd gebeten <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_114_r2l18">von ſölcher freẏheit vnd gnaden wegen die vvir von 
<del rend="strikethrough">ſeliger gedehtenüſſe </del> ~ <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_114_r2l20">voꝛdern / <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> gnedıgen <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_114_r2l19">ſeliger gedehtnüſſe </ab></add> in ewren <expan>land<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd herſchäften <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / darümb </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_114_r2l21">etliche <expan>vnſe<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> vnd kauffleute <expan>yecʒund<ex>en</ex></expan> cʒu <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>fürſtenlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_114_r2l22"> <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd 
<del rend="strikethrough">damit r dauon reden werden </del> mit <expan>denſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> dauon </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_114_r2l23">reden werden / <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr von <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden die <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> / durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_114_r2l24">vvılligen dinſte willen <expan>gütlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>hören</expan> / vnd <expan>gnedıklıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_114_line_1576568516423_1463"><expan>d<ex>ur</ex>hleuht<ex>ikeit</ex></expan> <expan>vertige<ex>n</ex></expan> wöllet Als etc das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc </ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter"><ab facs="#facs_114_r2l27">Hercʒog <expan>Albr<ex>echt</ex></expan> <expan>ſı<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_114" id="56v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Herczog Ernsten von Österreich </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Gnediger <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als wir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>durchleuhtik<ex>eit</ex></expan> vormals
                            <expan>verschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und gebeten
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von sölcher freyheit und gnaden wegen, die
                        wir von <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> vordern, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                        gnedigen <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, <add>seliger gedehtnüsse</add> in
                        ewren <expan>land<ex>en</ex></expan> und herschäften
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, darümb etliche
                            <expan>unse<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> und kauffleute
                            <expan>yeczund<ex>en</ex></expan> czu <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürstenlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> und mit <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> davon reden werden.
                            <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir von <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
                        gnaden die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> durch
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> willigen dinste willen
                                <expan>gütlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>hören</expan> und <expan>gnediklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        von <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>ur</ex>hleuht<ex>ikeit</ex></expan>
<expan>vertige<ex>n</ex></expan> wöllet, als etc. Das
                            <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. </ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter">
<ab>Herczog <expan>Albr<ex>echt</ex></expan>
<expan>si<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan>. </ab>
</div>
